text: Andries Nicolaas "Andy" den Houting was a cyclist from Canada. Andries competed at the 1928 Summer Olympics. He was born on 1 November 1901 and died on 2 December 1975.Andy Houting == References == Category:1901 births Category:1975 deaths Category:Canadian cyclists Category:Olympians for Canada Category:Sportspeople from Haarlem
